# ==========================
# CREAR CLIENTES
# ==========================

### Crear cliente válido 1
POST http://localhost:8001/api/clientes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": null,
  "dni": "12345678",
  "nombre": "Juan",
  "apellido": "Perez",
  "telefono": "555-1234",
  "direccion": "Calle Falsa 123"
}

### Crear cliente válido 2
